**Challenges:** 📈 L1 bidding · 📜 GeM + Make in India preference policies · ⚙ Installation and training at remote government offices · 🕐 Procurement cycles slow.

**Mistake:** Supplying without after-sales support. Government offices in remote areas need local support. Vendors who provide local maintenance win repeat orders.

**One-liner:** Supply IT to government — local after-sales support in remote areas wins repeat orders.

