**Challenges:** 📜 ISI/BIS standards for government furniture · ⚙ Delivery to multiple locations across districts · 💰 Working capital for large orders · 🕐 Payment delays.

**Mistake:** Using cheap materials to maximize margin. Government inspectors reject furniture that doesn't meet specifications. Quality testing certificates are inspected.

**One-liner:** Supply government furniture — quality testing certificates are checked; cheap materials get rejected on inspection.

