**Model:** Product Sale 📦 | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium.

**Challenges:** 📜 Rate contracts with OEMs · 📈 Only authorized dealers can bid · 💰 Large fleet orders · 🕐 Slow procurement · ⚙ Registration and documentation.

**Mistake:** Not becoming an authorized dealer first. Government vehicle procurement goes through OEM-authorized dealers only.

**One-liner:** Supply vehicles to government — must be an OEM-authorized dealer; government buys only through authorized channels.

